data.title: Mishti (Short 2023)
data.meta_description: Mishti: Directed by Akriti Singh. With Dilshad Patel, Akriti Singh. Whose souls live in the heart of our cities? A ghostly presence that refuses to be forgotten. A newly hired waitress without a name tag. The 'Story' has spirits lurking among the Urban Bustle. Lest you visit a cafe after watching.
